WEBVTT

00:01.627 --> 00:02.309
<i>(Banging on door)</i>

00:02.360 --> 00:04.395
Tucker: Hey! Hey, little help?

00:04.430 --> 00:07.164
Hey, the bathroom door is stuck again, guys!

00:07.200 --> 00:08.265
Ben: Emma?

00:08.301 --> 00:10.201
People, we got a runner.

00:10.236 --> 00:11.318
A pint-sized runner.

00:11.370 --> 00:12.937
Oh, there you are!

00:12.972 --> 00:14.972
- Hey.
- Hi!

00:15.024 --> 00:18.008
Dude, last night she climbed out
of her crib for the first time,

00:18.060 --> 00:20.611
and then gave me a
"what are you gonna do about it?" Look.

00:20.646 --> 00:21.946
What am I gonna do about it?

00:21.981 --> 00:23.447
(Banging continues)

00:23.482 --> 00:24.598
Tucker: Hey, is somebody out there?

00:24.650 --> 00:27.418
He baby-proofed the door
backwards and wrong.

00:27.453 --> 00:28.719
So, Tucker's in and can't get out.

00:28.771 --> 00:32.122
I would help him,
but I'm very busy enjoying this breakfast.

00:32.158 --> 00:33.324
Hey, speaking of breakfast,

00:33.359 --> 00:36.894
hey, do we have any non...

00:36.946 --> 00:38.996
okay. You know what?

00:39.031 --> 00:42.933
If this is another takeout menu from
the Chinese place, we will have words.

00:43.920 --> 00:44.869
It's a note.

00:46.706 --> 00:48.539
"Hear ye, hear ye, listen close,

00:48.574 --> 00:50.774
"in just one day, a birthday toast.

00:50.810 --> 00:52.643
"It's Bonnie Wheeler's special day,

00:52.678 --> 00:54.578
"so whoop it up, or you'll all pay.

00:54.630 --> 00:57.181
"Signed, anonymous."

00:57.216 --> 00:59.216
Man, I really thought it was from mom.

00:59.252 --> 01:01.185
Dude, oh my God!

01:01.220 --> 01:03.938
I promised mom a birthday party!
You know what this means?

01:03.990 --> 01:05.589
You have some things to plan?

01:05.625 --> 01:08.826
Yeah. Like, where to rent a getaway car,
or buy a ticket to anywhere but here.

01:08.828 --> 01:11.528
Emma? Emma? Where is she?

01:11.564 --> 01:13.380
- Hi.
- Hi.

01:13.416 --> 01:14.865
Tucker: Good news.

01:14.901 --> 01:17.368
At least one person around here
knows how to open a baby-proof door.

01:17.403 --> 01:18.552
Give me high-five!

01:18.604 --> 01:19.637
Yeah!

01:19.639 --> 01:22.373
(Theme music plays)

01:22.408 --> 01:25.442
